features: 【US to European Travel Plug Adapter】The Type C travel adapter is compatible in most European countries such as Austria, Belarus, Belgium, Croatia, Denmark, Finland, Germany, Greece, Hungary, Iceland, Italy, Netherlands, Portugal, Poland, Spain, Turkey and more. NOTE: NOT work in UK/Ireland/Scotland.

【7 in 1 EU Power Adapter】AnnTane European plug adapter turns 1 European Type C socket into 4 standard American outlets, 2 USB-A and 1 USB-C charging ports; Max capacity up to 3250 watt (250V/13A), larger space makes power adapter Europe easier to fit all electric equipment without blocking.

【European Travel Essentials】This International power adapter is compact and lightweight for easy travel and packing, no need to carry extra adapter or power strip for your traveling; A small US to Europe plug adapter can save your suitcase space, the indicator for reminding the Europe power adapter is on/off.

【Fast and Smart USB Charging】Dual USB A ports can charge up to 2.4A, and the USB C port can charge up to 3A; Ideal for cell phone, tablet, power bank, laptop, camera, etc; Note: All the USB ports output: 5V/3.4A, 17W max.

【Not a Voltage Converter】This type c plug adapter is only compatible for 100V-250V wide voltage device, if you want to use your hair dryer, straightener, electric toothbrush or razor, they MUST support 100V to 250V dual voltage, otherwise you may need a voltage converter.

【Quality Assurance】Certified by CE and FCC to ensure the quality, premium Internal metal interfaces offer good conductivity and this European power adapter have worry-free warranty and friendly customer service. Any problem with it, please contact us.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 23, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I'm thrilled with my purchase, as it proved incredibly useful during my trip to Portugal. In hindsight, I wish I had brought two, especially since I stayed at an Airbnb. Having an extra would have added significant convenience for my stay.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars perfect for travel
reviews.reviewText: The price was great for the value. I used this for my Europe trip that lasted a little more than a month. It's great for charging my phone, laptop, and steam deck. It comes with a little drawstring bag which is a bonus. No issues or problems yet

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works very well!
reviews.reviewText: I bought this European travel adapter for a trip to Europe. It worked beautifully, and I had no issues with it at all. As a bonus, on the cruise ship I was able to use an American version of this and the European version of this so we had plenty of outlets. Well made good quality product

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 27, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I took this to Spain and it was a a lifesaver for my friend as she forgot hers and didn't want to buy a new one It has 4 places to plug into and 2 USB ports. Plenty for the both of us to get charged up and ready to go.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Lots of outlets
reviews.reviewText: Ordered this for traveling to the EU. Have not been over there to test it yet but have tested it off the 110V here in the US (The USBs still worked even though this is not a voltage convertor!)I love the amount of outlets on this adapter and believe we'll have no issues on our travels based on testing here at home. The only criticism I have is that the 2 pin AC outlets are a little on the looser side than some of the adapters we have. Still safe and not a big deal.A small note on some of the negative reviews. The product page allows you to purchase two types of this adaptor Type C (for most of Europe) and Type G (for UK/Ireland). You can also choose to order a pack of 1 or a pack of two. When you place your order make sure you are ordering what you want - both quantity and type. Ordering a Type G and then complaining it doesn't work in Europe is not a product fault.. it's a user fault. Ordering a pack of 1 and then complaining you don't get two is not a poor product description.... you get the picture.These things work and if you like the look of the design you'll get what you order. No issues here. Solid. 4 stars.

reviews.reviewTitle: Will be useful on our upcoming cruise
reviews.reviewText: Purchased this adapter for use on an upcoming cruise. Since most cruise ships have limited amount of plugs - some North American style and some UK-style. This should allow us to use the UK-style plugs while on our cruise. :)
